reviewText: V​ery poorly designed course. No pauses. No example scenarios. Non-stop speed talker. This course violates almost every guide line for on-line learning.

T​his course is hard to follow. It basically is just a dictionary being thrown at you. It doesnt seem relatable or useful because all it talks about "NIST Special publication..." one after the next. I get it, the sources are important but real examples of how to apply the knowledge are more useful because I feel like I havent learned anything.... literally.
Excellent fundamental breakdown of the RMF.
